title: GotoNassau
body:
[img]/assets/data-models/stories/20201000029_nassau/jannassau.png[/img]

"You took your time!

Do you know who I am? 

Why didn't you save me earlier?

Don't you know I have other things to do!"

[[Be thankful that I saved you at all. I can also re-petrify you if you're unhappy.|YouAchterlijkeGladiool]] [[Tell me more.|Nottime]]

title: Nottime
body:
[img]/assets/data-models/stories/20201000029_nassau/jannassau.png[/img]

"You plebs!

"Can't you see that I'm the brother of William of Orange?

My time is too valuable to waste on you.

I have the Union of Utrecht to sign!"


[i]Nassau looks in his pocket for the Union of Utrecht but he cannot find the declaration.[/i]

"Huh? Where did go?"

[[ Give Union of Utrecht|givedeclarationtonassau]]

title: YouAchterlijkeGladiool
body:
[img]/assets/data-models/stories/20201000029_nassau/jannassau.png[/img]

"You Achterlijke Gladiool!

How dare you talk to me this way?!

Do you want to be under the Spanish occupation?

We need to unite the northern provinces."

 [[Give Union of Utrecht |givedeclarationtonassau]]

title: givedeclarationtonassau
body:
[img]/assets/data-models/stories/20201000029_nassau/jannassau.png[/img]

"You dief! How did you steal it?"

[i]Nassau does not give you time to respond. [/i]

[i]He signs the declaration with a quill, throws it on the ground after using it, and leaves.[/i]
[[pick up quill|pick up quill button]]
